metadata.name: Synesthesia Sounding
metadata.description: The journey now begins with a mysterious place shrouded in a vacuum, the universe talking to each other emits a language in the form of sound that we digest, using only one ear, go into this work, then you will meet an inner depth , the parent receptor of the contents of the head, leads to an objectivity of color and form, coupled with the rhythm, and the pressure of the sound generated by the abstractly created tone, this work is a sign that in fact the universe is indeed endless, even every second has something unique. unpredictable, even mysterious.
